Mark C. Vadon, MBA

Age : 47Public asset : 153,620,287 USDLinked companies :  Home Depot Inc -  Liberty Interactive QVC Group 





Summary 



Mr. Mark C. Vadon is Chairman at Chewy.com LLC.He is on the Board of Directors at Liberty Interactive Corp. and The Home Depot, Inc. Mr. Vadon was previously employed as Chairman by zulily, Inc., Chairman by zulily LLC, Chairman by Blue Nile, Inc., and a Consultant by Bain & Co., Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from Harvard University and an MBA from Stanford University.



