Insider Activity


Individual




Mark C. Vadon



Mr. Mark C. Vadon is Independent Director at The Home Depot, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Liberty Interactive Corp. and The Home Depot, Inc. 
Mr. Vadon was previously employed as Chairman by zulily, Inc., Chairman by Blue Nile, Inc., a Consultant by Bain & Co., Inc., and an Advisor by Maveron LLC. 
He received his undergraduate degree from Harvard University and an MBA from Stanford University.



